                        <interp inst="t18361024-name-984" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE BASCOMBE</persName>
                  </hi>. This is the spoon—part of the crest is obtained—I had asked the prisoner if he had seen it in the wash?—he said he had not—I offered him 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. if he could find it.</p>
               <p>(James Walton, of Richmond, gave the prisoner a good character, and promised to take him into his employ).</p>
